{
 "name": "RPlog_Mayhem_Aboard_OS_Paladin",
 "title": "Mayhem Aboard OS Paladin",
 "summary": "In the main hangar bay of the New Republic station OS Paladin, Commander Kyrin Sh'vani oversees a team trying to crack open a heavily shielded, booby-trapped cargo container of unknown contents. Her bored Marines, led by the brash Lieutenant Vengan Draelis and the green Twi'lek Sergeant Tal'sin Secura, lobby for thermite while the Bith technician Ohao works the lock and the pilot Raxis delivers coded orders fresh off his X-wing. When the technicians finally breach the seal, the container releases a horned Doashim and two Nexu that go on a killing rampage across the deck. Kyrin, Vengan, Raxis, and the Marines open fire, taking casualties before downing the beasts, after which the bloodied survivors lock down the hangar and call in medical and combat teams.",
